I asked. "Yes, Your Majesty. I come from that hive over there in a tree and we bees think you should be our queen" "I'm not a bee, I'm a human. And I'm allergic to bees!" "Yes, we know, but we think you're perfect for the job." sa

I asked. "Yes, Your Majesty. I come from that hive over there in a tree and we bees think you should be our queen" "I'm not a bee, I'm a human. And I'm allergic to bees!" "Yes, we know, but we think you're perfect for the job." said the little bee." "Well I do like your little suit. Maybe

I asked. "Yes, Your Majesty. I come from that hive over there in a tree and we bees think you should be our queen" "I'm not a bee, I'm a human. And I'm allergic to bees!" "Yes, we know, but we think you're perfect for the job." said the little bee." "Well I do like your little suit. Maybe I will consider. What do I have to do to be your queen

I asked. "Yes, Your Majesty. I come from that hive over there in a tree and we bees think you should be our queen" "I'm not a bee, I'm a human. And I'm allergic to bees!" "Yes, we know, but we think you're perfect for the job." said the little bee." "Well I do like your little suit. Maybe I will consider. What do I have to do to be your queen?", I asked. "You just have to do one thing. You have to make a wish and we will grant it." I thought that sure sounded ea

I asked. "Yes, Your Majesty. I come from that hive over there in a tree and we bees think you should be our queen" "I'm not a bee, I'm a human. And I'm allergic to bees!" "Yes, we know, but we think you're perfect for the job." said the little bee." "Well I do like your little suit. Maybe I will consider. What do I have to do to be your queen?", I asked. "You just have to do one thing. You have to make a wish and we will grant it." I thought that sure sounded easy. But I didn't know what wish to mak

I asked. "Yes, Your Majesty. I come from that hive over there in a tree and we bees think you should be our queen" "I'm not a bee, I'm a human. And I'm allergic to bees!" "Yes, we know, but we think you're perfect for the job." said the little bee." "Well I do like your little suit. Maybe I will consider. What do I have to do to be your queen?", I asked. "You just have to do one thing. You have to make a wish and we will grant it." I thought that sure sounded easy. But I didn't know what wish to make. After a few minutes I finally decided. "I wish I could fly like a bee." I said. "Your wish is granted." said the little bee. And I grew wings and became like a bee. I was able to fly around and it was fant

I asked. "Yes, Your Majesty. I come from that hive over there in a tree and we bees think you should be our queen" "I'm not a bee, I'm a human. And I'm allergic to bees!" "Yes, we know, but we think you're perfect for the job." said the little bee." "Well I do like your little suit. Maybe I will consider. What do I have to do to be your queen?", I asked. "You just have to do one thing. You have to make a wish and we will grant it." I thought that sure sounded easy. But I didn't know what wish to make. After a few minutes I finally decided. "I wish I could fly like a bee." I said. "Your wish is granted." said the little bee. And I grew wings and became like a bee. I was able to fly around and it was fantastic! "So what do you think?" as

I asked. "Yes, Your Majesty. I come from that hive over there in a tree and we bees think you should be our queen" "I'm not a bee, I'm a human. And I'm allergic to bees!" "Yes, we know, but we think you're perfect for the job." said the little bee." "Well I do like your little suit. Maybe I will consider. What do I have to do to be your queen?", I asked. "You just have to do one thing. You have to make a wish and we will grant it." I thought that sure sounded easy. But I didn't know what wish to make. After a few minutes I finally decided. "I wish I could fly like a bee." I said. "Your wish is granted." said the little bee. And I grew wings and became like a bee. I was able to fly around and it was fantastic! "So what do you think?" asked the Bee. Do you like being the

"I know but I didn't want to be a bee!" Little did I know that by making that wish I had resigned myself to a life of being the queen bee. I was stuck as a bee for the rest of my life. But I made the best of it and I was a really good queen bee.
